Class ElasticParticipantController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.psychic_engine.cmput301w17t10.feelsappman.Controllers.ElasticController

  • public class ElasticParticipantController
extends ElasticController
    ElasticParticipantController handles all elastic requests in regards to participants. Tasks will be used to editMoodEvent, add, and find participants to find other participants using the app. Comments by adong on 3/28/2017.
